    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Adam is a Brooklyn based filmmaker. His shooting adventures have taken him around the world. Most recently he photographed director Dream Hampton&rsquo;s second feature length documentary, TRANSPARENT &ndash; a film about the life of Shelly Hilliard, a transgender teenager from Detroit. Adam&rsquo;s award winning work has screened across the US, Europe, and Africa, including at home at the Museum of Contemporary African Diasporan Arts in Brooklyn.</p>

<p>In addition to feature length and short form work, he has edited branded content for clients such as: Chanel, Electus, Equinox Gyms, Comcast, Kiehls, and Atlantic Records.</p>

